iOS之来电阻止与身份识别实现 原创

2017-07-26 11:41:49

LVXIANGAN

码龄13年

关注

      为了屏蔽各种中介的电话骚扰，最近安装了腾讯手机管家，安装完成后，设置“骚扰拦截”功能时，App提示需要点击“设置--->电话--->来电阻止与身份识别--->勾选App提供的"黄页"、“电话识别”和“电话拦截”。



了解过苹果沙盒机制的朋友都知道，一般在App中要访问到其他 App/硬件（地理位置，相册，通讯录，话筒） 内容，会通过系统弹窗询问用户，必须要获取管理员许可才行，比如这样：



那么上面的“来电阻止和身份识别”功能又是什么东东呢？


CallKit.framework


苹果在iOS 10中为我们带来了callkit.framework，当我们语言通话显示系统界面时，它允许我们对来电号码进行识别、过滤、标记、阻止等操作。目前国内垃圾电话、骚扰电话、诈骗电话不胜其烦，针对iPhone全球第二大市场，苹果今次顺势而为推出开放接口，也算是人心所向。有兴趣的朋友可以通过官方文档说明了解callkit.framework。


下面我们尝试来写一个demo，让自己App出现在电话“设置--->电话--->来电阻止与身份识别 列表中，实现来电过滤功能

1、新建一个iOS工程




2、完成后，新建target：点击"+"---> 选择iOS，Call Directory Extension， 输入名称如：CallFirewall，一路next，选择“Activate”






3、完成上面操作，可以看到在项目工程中，自动生成了下面几个文件。



4、打开文件 CallDirectoryHandler.h 和 CallDirectoryHandler.m，使用注意事项，请参照代码注释：

  1. //
  2. //  CallDirectoryHandler.h
  3. //  CallFirewall
  4. //
  5. //  Created by lvxiangan on 26/07/2017.
  6. //  Copyright © 2017 lvxiangan. All rights reserved.
  7. //
  8.  
  9. #import <Foundation/Foundation.h>
  10. #import <CallKit/CallKit.h>
  11.  
  12. @interface CallDirectoryHandler : CXCallDirectoryProvider
  13.  
  14. @end
  1. //
  2. //  CallDirectoryHandler.m
  3. //  CallFirewall
  4. //
  5. //  Created by lvxiangan on 26/07/2017.
  6. //  Copyright © 2017 lvxiangan. All rights reserved.
  7. //
  8.  
  9. #import "CallDirectoryHandler.h"
  10.  
  11. @interface CallDirectoryHandler () <CXCallDirectoryExtensionContextDelegate>
  12. @end
  13.  
  14. @implementation CallDirectoryHandler
  15.  
  16. // 请求前检查
  17. - (void)beginRequestWithExtensionContext:(CXCallDirectoryExtensionContext *)context {
  18.     context.delegate = self;
  19.  
  20.     if (![self addBlockingPhoneNumbersToContext:context]) {
  21.         NSLog(@"Unable to add blocking phone numbers");
  22.         NSError *error = [NSError errorWithDomain:@"CallDirectoryHandler" code:1 userInfo:nil];
  23.         [context cancelRequestWithError:error];
  24.         return;
  25.     }
  26.     
  27.     if (![self addIdentificationPhoneNumbersToContext:context]) {
  28.         NSLog(@"Unable to add identification phone numbers");
  29.         NSError *error = [NSError errorWithDomain:@"CallDirectoryHandler" code:2 userInfo:nil];
  30.         [context cancelRequestWithError:error];
  31.         return;
  32.     }
  33.     
  34.     [context completeRequestWithCompletionHandler:nil];
  35. }
  36.  
  37.  
  38. // 来电阻止
  39. - (BOOL)addBlockingPhoneNumbersToContext:(CXCallDirectoryExtensionContext *)context {
  40.     // Retrieve phone numbers to block from data store. For optimal performance and memory usage when there are many phone numbers,
  41.     // consider only loading a subset of numbers at a given time and using autorelease pool(s) to release objects allocated during each batch of numbers which are loaded.
  42.     //
  43.     // Numbers must be provided in numerically ascending order.
  44.     CXCallDirectoryPhoneNumber phoneNumbers[] = { 14085555555, 18005555555 };
  45.     NSUInteger count = (sizeof(phoneNumbers) / sizeof(CXCallDirectoryPhoneNumber));
  46.  
  47.     for (NSUInteger index = 0; index < count; index += 1) {
  48.         CXCallDirectoryPhoneNumber phoneNumber = phoneNumbers[index];
  49.         [context addBlockingEntryWithNextSequentialPhoneNumber:phoneNumber];
  50.     }
  51.  
  52.     return YES;
  53. }
  54.  
  55.  
  56. // 来电识别
  57. - (BOOL)addIdentificationPhoneNumbersToContext:(CXCallDirectoryExtensionContext *)context {
  58.     // Retrieve phone numbers to identify and their identification labels from data store. For optimal performance and memory usage when there are many phone numbers,
  59.     // consider only loading a subset of numbers at a given time and using autorelease pool(s) to release objects allocated during each batch of numbers which are loaded.
  60.     //
  61.     // Numbers must be provided in numerically ascending order.
  62.     CXCallDirectoryPhoneNumber phoneNumbers[] = { 18775555555, 18885555555 };
  63.     NSArray<NSString *> *labels = @[ @"Telemarketer", @"Local business" ];
  64.     NSUInteger count = (sizeof(phoneNumbers) / sizeof(CXCallDirectoryPhoneNumber));
  65.  
  66.     for (NSUInteger i = 0; i < count; i += 1) {
  67.         CXCallDirectoryPhoneNumber phoneNumber = phoneNumbers[i];
  68.         NSString *label = labels[i];
  69.         [context addIdentificationEntryWithNextSequentialPhoneNumber:phoneNumber label:label];
  70.     }
  71.  
  72.     return YES;
  73. }
  74.  
  75. #pragma mark - CXCallDirectoryExtensionContextDelegate
  76.  
  77. // 添加黑名单或识别来电失败处理
  78. - (void)requestFailedForExtensionContext:(CXCallDirectoryExtensionContext *)extensionContext withError:(NSError *)error {
  79.     // An error occurred while adding blocking or identification entries, check the NSError for details.
  80.     // For Call Directory error codes, see the CXErrorCodeCallDirectoryManagerError enum in <CallKit/CXError.h>.
  81.     //
  82.     // This may be used to store the error details in a location accessible by the extension's containing app, so that the
  83.     // app may be notified about errors which occured while loading data even if the request to load data was initiated by
  84.     // the user in Settings instead of via the app itself.
  85. }
  86.  
  87. @end





同理，参照腾讯手机管家的做法，我们建多几个target，就会在“来电阻止与身份识别”中有多个选项。




这样，我们就可以根据自定义target用途，来编写不同功能的代码了。
